Retrieve Malawi country boundaries

Source: R/get_boundaries.R
get_country.Rd

Retrieve Malawi country boundaries

get_country(layer = get_boundaries_name(adm = 0))

Arguments

layer

Name of layer for country boundaries

Value

An sf object for the country borders of Malawi

Examples
